FBIS4-14748 "drsov064_f_94034" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 National Affairs Gas Supplies to Indebted Enterprises To Cease 10 Apr Gas Supplies to Indebted Enterprises To Cease 10 Apr LD0104111594 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 0900 GMT 1 Apr 94 LD0104111594 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Ukrainian BFN [Text] The supply of gas to enterprises in debt that cannot pay for the gas they have consumed will stop on 10 April in accordance with a resolution on enterprises' payments for natural gas, passed by Ukraine's Cabinet of Ministers.
